    "description": "Qualtec Co.,Ltd. engages in the defect analysis and reliability testing of electronic components in Japan. It operates through Reliability Evaluation Business and Microfabrication Business segments. The company offers microfabrication on laser processing and surface treatment plating technologies. It also provides reliability evaluation tests, such as environmental tests, electrical tests, and vibration tests for electronic components, failure analysis of defective products, cross-sectional sample preparation, package resin opening, and manufacturing and sales of testing machines. In addition, the company performs prototype and mass production laser processing for build-up boards, flexible printed circuit boards, etc., as well as genetic testing services for detecting gene mutations causing genetic diseases in dogs and cats, as well as contract testing services for bio-medical products, such as packaging materials and syringes. Further, it offers various consulting services. Qualtec Co.,Ltd. was incorporated in 1993 and is headquartered in Sakai, Japan."
